src="http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js"></script> </p><div class="clear"></div> &nbsp;<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://kotovski.net/o-kotovskom/" rel="nofollow"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-10616" alt="podpis-12" src="http://kotovski.net/wp-content/uploads/podpis-12.jpg" width="600" height="100" /></a></p><div class="post-entry-bottom"></div></div><div id="comments"><h3><font color="5b5a5a">Ваши комментарии к статье:</font></h3><dl class="tabs"><dt class="selected">Сайт Котовского</dt><dd class="selected"><div class="tab-content"><div id="commentsbox"><h3 id="comments">57 Комментариев</h3><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-43946"><div id="comment-43946" class="comment-body"><div class="comment-avatar"> <img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/c891b0181483a7e7ce845448f107e7bb?s=50&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/c891b0181483a7e7ce845448f107e7bb?s=100&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-50 photo' height='50' width='50' /></div><div class="comment-author vcard"> <cite class="fn">Наталья</cite><span class="says">:</span> - <span class="comment-reply"></span></div><div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"> <a href="http://kotovski.net/skolko-zarabatyivaet-velosipednyiy-vor-v-anglii/#comment-43946">01.09.2015 в 06:53</a></div><p>Доброго времени суток! Вопрос не по теме, но может подскажите где в Паттайе можно купить или арендовать велосипеды?</p></div></li><li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-43947"><div id="comment-43947" class="comment-body"><div class="comment-avatar"> <img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/4509db82a4566425138455925df9ae01?s=50&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/4509db82a4566425138455925df9ae01?s=100&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-50 photo' height='50' width='50' /></div><div class="comment-author vcard"> <cite class="fn">Михаил</cite><span clas